@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Light Tips";
}

<div class="container py-4">
    <h1>☀ Light Tips</h1>

    <div class="card mt-3">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">How light affects plant health</h5>

            <p>
                Light is one of the most important factors for healthy plant growth.
                Different plant types need different light intensity and duration.
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li><strong>Succulents and cacti</strong> usually prefer strong direct light.</li>
                <li><strong>Orchids</strong> often do best in bright indirect light.</li>
                <li><strong>Tropical plants</strong> usually prefer medium to bright indirect light.</li>
                <li><strong>Air plants</strong> need bright but filtered light.</li>
            </ul>

            <p>
                Too little light can cause weak growth and pale leaves.
                Too much direct sunlight can burn the leaves.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>